burlap.behavior.singleagent.learnfromdemo.mlirl.differentiableplanners.diffvinit

Class LinearStateDiffVF

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.behavior.singleagent.learnfromdemo.mlirl.differentiableplanners.diffvinit.DifferentiableVInit.ParamedDiffVInit
      • burlap.behavior.singleagent.learnfromdemo.mlirl.differentiableplanners.diffvinit.LinearStateDiffVF
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DifferentiableVInit, ValueFunction, ValueFunctionInitialization

    public class LinearStateDiffVF
extends DifferentiableVInit.ParamedDiffVInit
    A class for defining a (differentiable) linear function over state features for value function initialization. This class is useful for learning the value function initialization for leaf nodes of a finite horizon valueFunction with MLIRL.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan.
